Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{=4}---- Dialogue
Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.94,0:00:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you just say?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:03.02,0:00:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ayane{**-chan}, c-could you repeat that one more time?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.86,0:00:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}, calm down, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:09.24,0:00:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} calm!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.78,0:00:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She's right, Serika!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.70,0:00:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We shouldn't panic!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.33,0:00:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}, you're shaking.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.04,0:00:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane{**-chan}, are you sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.87,0:00:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.92,0:00:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I went through all the documents we acquired,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.46,0:00:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and it definitely seems that Kaiser Loans\nhas been funding the Helmet Gang.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.93,0:00:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.72,0:00:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.43,0:00:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's really true,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.76,0:00:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,then those jerks from the Helmet Gang,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.39,0:00:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the same people who've been trying to gun us down,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.40,0:00:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,have been buying their weapons using {\i1}our{\i0} money!
Comment: 10,0:02:17.24,0:02:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hoshino noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.33,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, there it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.16,0:02:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Collected 7.88 million yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, isn't this...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It's exactly what you think it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.54,0:02:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something special about\nthis 7.88 million yen entry?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.76,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, could this be...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.59,0:02:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. This is the exact amount we paid them.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.31,0:02:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,7.88 million is a lot.\nYou were in that much debt?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.81,0:02:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is only a fraction. The total is over 900 million.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.48,0:02:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, we can get into\nthe finer details some other time.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.53,0:02:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This document lists all of Kaiser Loans's cash flows.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.95,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we see a figure that matches\nour 7.88 million payment down to the yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.49,0:03:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to have come from\nthe debt collector that visits our school.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.29,0:03:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's this.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.42,0:03:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right after depositing the 7.88 million yen,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.00,0:03:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,they allocated five million yen towards\n"strategic allocations" to the Kata-Kata Helmet Gang.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Strategic allocations...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.30,0:03:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They sent the Kata-Kata Helmet Gang\nfive million yen to help fund their job.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Job?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.64,0:03:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was probably to take us out of the picture.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.44,0:03:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.02,0:03:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It means Kaiser Loans has been\nour real enemy all along!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would they do this?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If the school went bankrupt,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.08,0:03:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,they wouldn't be able to get back\nthe money they loaned us.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you say Kaiser Loans?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.84,0:03:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(5170,5600,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}They're the loan sharks run by\nthe infamous Kaiser Corporation, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.09,0:04:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt Kaiser Loans is acting on its own.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.02,0:04:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaiser Corporation's main branch\nmust be involved in this as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:08.35,0:04:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.81,0:04:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me earlier!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.32,0:04:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it. If anything, we should be\napologising for dragging you into our mess.
Comment: 10,0:04:19.45,0:04:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahaha {hifumi_laugh.jpeg --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.41,0:04:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'll report this situation to the Tea Party.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.71,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kaiser Corporation must have ties to criminals\nand other underground dealings.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.09,0:04:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And this could help prove it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.26,0:04:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, now that I've gotten to know you,\nI can't leave you to fend for yourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.01,0:04:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate it!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.64,0:04:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If Trinity's student council could lend us a hand,\nwe'd be in a much better position.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.10,0:04:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.80,0:04:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, this has been quite a shock.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.03,0:04:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're a billion yen in debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.90,0:05:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not {\i1}that{\i0} much! It's only 960 mil—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}, she was just rounding it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.58,0:05:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-In any case, I'm sure once\nthe Tea Party hears about this—
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.21,0:05:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure it's old news to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.79,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And not just over at the Tea Party.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet the hotshots over at Gehenna\nand Millennium all know already.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.76,0:05:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? But if they know what's going on, then why?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.97,0:05:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They knew, and simply turned a blind eye to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But why would they...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.93,0:05:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you mean well, and I appreciate it,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.64,0:05:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but the world just ain't that simple.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.15,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you went ahead and told them,\nit might just complicate things for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.19,0:05:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.65,0:05:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it. Abydos High is\non the verge of shutting down, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.57,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a whole lot's gonna stop these schools\nfrom asking us to "return the favour" for helping us.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm getting at?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.79,0:05:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, basically, if they said they'd help\nbut then took advantage of the situation,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.63,0:06:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you would be powerless to stop them?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.72,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.84,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}, aren't you being a little cynical?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.22,0:06:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We could use all the help we can get.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.85,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.64,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's always the off chance, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The off chance...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.61,0:06:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, this is a tough one.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.53,0:06:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.32,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'll find a way.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.99,0:06:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be {\i1}something{\i0} we can do, r-right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, c'mon!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Show at least a {\i1}little{\i0} conviction!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.33,0:06:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, thinking about this logically...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.46,0:06:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then quit thinking.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.38,0:06:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, everyone was looking at me, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.01,0:06:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Of course everyone was gonna look at you with that timing.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.72,0:06:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}C'mon, you should be used to this by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.35,0:06:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And anyway you're—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.26,0:06:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{*}Teacher{*Sensei} is doing the best he can to help us.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.88,0:06:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The off chance, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's precisely because we neglected\nthe off chance that Abydos ended up like this.
Comment: 10,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hoshino noises}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.73,0:07:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, let this old soul in on the fun.\nWhat's all the chatter about?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't believe this.\nHifumi{**-san} was just saying—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.99,0:07:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying what? Mind repeating it, Faust{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.82,0:07:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop calling me that!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.66,0:07:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The great mastermind\nbehind the Masked Swimsuit Gang!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.58,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I am most definitely {\i1}not{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, quit picking on Hifumi!
Comment: 10,0:07:16.50,0:07:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hifumi_laugh.jpeg --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I should get going.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Today was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.13,0:07:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure {\i1}you{\i0} had fun,\nbut what about the rest of us?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.09,0:07:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll drop by one of these days,\nso let's hang out sometime.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hifumi, good luck out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.31,0:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's tough, but I'm cheering for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.98,0:07:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye for now!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.15,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we'll really be okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.70,0:07:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's not dwell on it anymore for today.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.12,0:07:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all tuckered out.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.25,0:07:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, let's meet back up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.33,0:08:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home and rest up for today, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.50,0:08:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.38,0:08:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(3046,4088,\c&H000000&)}Staying up late's bad for the skin, y'know?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.97,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.68,0:08:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good m—Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.11,0:08:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aru{**-chan}, were you up all night or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.82,0:08:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I caught a few winks.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.07,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aru{**-chan}. We've come up\nwith a new plan to attack Abydos.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Kayoko{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.87,0:08:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We plant explosives in key locations ahead of time,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.96,0:08:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and when they get near them,\nwe blow them to kingdom come.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka's out making preparations...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.72,0:08:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.68,0:08:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I heard you!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.39,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.26,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about some things.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.47,0:08:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just to be sure, can we go ahead with this plan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.77,0:08:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, if you're losing sleep over it,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.86,0:09:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't we just take the money\nthey left behind and put it towards our funds?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.78,0:09:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.07,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This money is something\nthose girls left behind by accident.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.16,0:09:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Using it would just be uncool.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,True outlaws wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.04,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't we get an advance from the client?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.75,0:09:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No upfront payments.\nThat's the one policy I refuse to break.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been over this, haven't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.79,0:09:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because accepting payment in advance\nmeans we're forced to comply with their demands.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Comment: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{Mesugaki noises} {who is responsible for this --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.47,0:09:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, that may ring a bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We only take money for\na job well done. No exceptions.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.43,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If we waver, we'll never achieve the vision\nwe've strived towards for so long.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.31,0:09:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Our vision? We have one?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.78,0:09:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we do!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.73,0:09:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a group of hard-boiled outlaws,\nunshackled by rules or laws!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.49,0:09:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the vision of Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.83,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, boss, we could always just\nthrow in the towel and go back to Gehenna.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.87,0:10:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't the Prefect Team\nbe all over us if we did that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.04,0:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point. The Prefect Team would be a problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.88,0:10:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A {\i1}big{\i0} problem. They're the\nstrongest team in all of Kivotos, no?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.93,0:10:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but only because of the Head Prefect, Hina.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.68,0:10:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no exaggeration to say the bulk\nof their firepower comes from just her.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.19,0:10:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.77,0:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the rest of them should be easy pickings.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.78,0:10:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Confident, are we?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, only if we play our cards right.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.03,0:10:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Going back to Gehenna is not an option.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.54,0:10:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not for a group of hard-boiled outlaws,\nunshackled by rules or laws.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.08,0:10:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Problem Solver 68's\nvision or whatever, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Haruka.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.01,0:10:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Had fun out there?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.26,0:11:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Comment: 10,0:11:01.72,0:11:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Aru, just give me the word.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say the word.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.19,0:11:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll blow it all to smithereens for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,With my own two hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.95,0:11:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, Aru{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like someone's hungry!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.12,0:11:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Shut it, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.70,0:11:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna grab a bite?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Let's.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.70,0:11:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we thinking?\nRamen over at Shiba Seki?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.17,0:11:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the part-timer.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.63,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She only works in the afternoon, so we're good.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.96,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then. Come on, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Haruka{**-chan}. We're leaving.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, coming.
Comment: 10,0:11:42.14,0:11:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{yawn.jpeg}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're early today.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, {*}Teach{*Sensei}.{OJISAAAAAAAAAAN} {I sense a remarkable force behind this comment --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.65,0:11:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two doing here this early?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.90,0:11:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I've got dibs on this lap.\nThis is my special napping spot.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I wasn't going to join you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.99,0:12:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon now, Hoshino{**-senpai}.\nThere's enough lap for both of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really. I wasn't going to join her...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Upsy daisy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's my day off.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.59,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go kill time somewhere else,\nso give me a holler if you need me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.18,0:12:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose she's off to take a nap?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the perfect weather for one.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}'s changed a lot.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.82,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She acts like a lazy sleepyhead nowadays,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.36,0:12:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but back when I first met her,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.28,0:12:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,she always looked like she was\nweighed down by something.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.08,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Weighed down? By what?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.70,0:12:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything and everything, I suppose.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.08,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I heard, back when Hoshino{**-senpai} enrolled,\nthere used to be another older student here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.55,0:12:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, she was the last\nstudent council president Abydos ever had.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.30,0:13:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So once she was gone,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.51,0:13:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai} ended up shouldering\nall the responsibilities alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.60,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She was only a first-year at the time, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.56,0:13:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if that was why,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.56,0:13:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's always been against\ninvolving other schools.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.78,0:13:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's mellowed out a lot since then.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.45,0:13:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like I was there,\nso I only know so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.62,0:13:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because I'm here now?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.29,0:13:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.71,0:13:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why she changed.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.96,0:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.46,0:13:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean, you know...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm trying to say is...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.98,0:13:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sure you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks fer waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.70,0:14:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking forward to this!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O-One bowl per person?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.92,0:14:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really okay for us to have all this?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.38,0:14:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry 'bout it.\nY'all came all the way over just for my ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.47,0:14:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What more's there to say?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.05,0:14:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you so much!\nFrom the bottom of my heart!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.10,0:14:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.56,0:14:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We really can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.40,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.44,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cherish every single bite.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.23,0:14:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give ya a li'l extra on the house,\nso eat your fill, y'hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.49,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend o' Serika{**-chan}'s a friend o' mine.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.37,0:14:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange how it's so empty when the food's this good.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.09,0:15:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it just the location?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.05,0:15:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,People have been leaving\nbecause of the desertification, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.55,0:15:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.01,0:15:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not their friends!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're making a scene.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.93,0:15:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.60,0:15:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've figured out what my problem is.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this restaurant!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you liked the ramen here.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I do!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This place has good food,\ngives very generous portions,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.24,0:15:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people here are nothing but nice!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.20,0:15:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's the problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.07,0:15:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see? All of it!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.74,0:15:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here on business!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.29,0:15:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to be hard-boiled outlaws!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.29,0:15:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But this cozy atmosphere is turning us\ninto {\i1}soft{\i0}-boiled outlaws! {A+ --ik}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.05,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be honest, you've lost me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.67,Alt,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,***,Haruka?
Comment: 10,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,***,Haruka-chan?
Comment: 10,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.72,Alt,,0,0,0,***,Haruka?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.72,0:15:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand what I'm trying to say, Haruka?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.34,0:15:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.30,0:15:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying this restaurant should go, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.68,0:15:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.64,0:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, could you clarify what you mean by "go"?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what I said. It has to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.27,0:16:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.98,0:16:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.70,0:16:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.20,0:16:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Haruka!
Comment: 10,0:16:12.41,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{boom.jpeg}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.41,0:16:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been an explosion in town,\nten kilometres from here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The blast site is...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.34,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,***,Ayane?
Comment: 10,0:16:23.34,0:16:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,***,Ayane-chan?
Comment: 10,0:16:23.34,0:16:24.84,Alt,,0,0,0,***,Ayane?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.46,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The blast site is at Shiba Seki Ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.43,0:16:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would anyone target that place?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.97,0:16:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What—No, {\i1}who{\i0} are they after?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.85,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be Serika{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.60,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We can figure that out once we get there!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let her know.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.65,0:16:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to hurry and help the boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.15,0:16:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.16,0:16:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold on, boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.78,0:16:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.84,0:17:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,There's our Aru{**-chan}. Found her!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.89,0:17:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutsuki, Kayoko…
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.60,0:17:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Boss?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Haruka?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.10,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be somewhere around here.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.52,0:17:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she planted C4\nat the ramen shop of all places...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.07,0:17:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, speaking of, what even was the plan with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you this morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.20,0:17:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Except this bit wasn't part of the plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.58,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what now?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.91,0:17:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.92,0:17:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, think about it.\nWasn't this exactly what you wanted?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted the restaurant gone, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.92,0:17:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Actually, I-I was the one who said that.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.05,0:17:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka, are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm completely fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.14,0:17:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But more importantly, {*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.06,0:18:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I perhaps just made things worse?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.27,0:18:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be better to have\nmore explosives in more places, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point I should just die for my...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe later.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,First things first, we should talk about...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.50,0:18:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Looking at this situation...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.38,0:18:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we the baddies? We are, aren't we?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.59,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.67,0:18:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission accomplished, no?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.34,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.47,0:18:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, weren't you scared you were becoming a softie?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After everything those nice people did for you,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.60,0:18:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you were so terrified you'd grow a conscience,\nyou decided to blow up the entire place.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.98,0:18:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as cold-blooded and {**\n}ruthless as they come, Aru{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.32,0:18:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right! No morals! No mercy!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.62,0:18:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay us the dime and we do the crime!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.33,0:19:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our motto!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.25,0:19:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.79,0:19:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well, if it isn't the\ncute little part-timer from Shiba Seki Ramen.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.38,0:19:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You four... What do you think you're doing there?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.18,0:19:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows. Why don't you take a guess?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.01,0:19:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you the ones who blew up Shiba Seki Ramen?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.27,0:19:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if we were?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.02,0:19:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll respond with appropriate force.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard the girl, Aru{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.65,0:19:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it'd be so soon,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.15,0:19:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but we were going to have to\nsettle the score one of these days anyway.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.74,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll make it right to you\nthis time, {*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}! I promise!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-Wh-Wh-What now?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.46,0:19:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I just come clean and give an honest apology?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.29,0:19:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if I do, Problem Solver 68's reputation...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.96,0:19:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our {\i0}pride{\i1} as outlaws is toast!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.55,0:19:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop beating around the bush!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.43,0:20:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us a straight answer!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.35,0:20:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Q-Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.06,0:20:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.56,0:20:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones who blew up Shiba Seki Ramen\nwere none other than us,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.73,0:20:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally get the picture now?\nWe're bad to the bone!{rotating skull.gif -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.07,0:20:18.32,Alt,,0,0,0,,Aru{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.62,0:20:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.16,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The boss is secure!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.46,0:20:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Only minor injuries!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll escort him to the nearest shelter.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.92,0:20:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rendezvous with you after!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.42,0:20:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad he's okay, Serika{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.88,0:20:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Too damn far.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.51,0:20:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not calming down this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.93,0:20:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.90,0:20:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, then! Have at you!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.36,0:20:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dead! {don't drop the f bomb, don't drop the f bomb... --ik}{i mean, surely the show's at least PG13, we can drop one or two -p}{let the cat say fuck! --ML}{## fuck the cat—wait}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.04,0:21:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, what now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's them.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Them"?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.71,0:21:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But why now of all times?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.13,0:21:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}! Please, wake up!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.63,0:21:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}! {*}Miss Aru{*Aru-sama}!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.18,0:21:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.35,0:21:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.02,0:21:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,For the love of—Now what?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.56,0:21:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.56,0:21:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we've been shelled by someone up ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.32,0:21:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Targets appear to be in disarray\nfollowing our mortar strike.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.95,0:21:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, how should we do this, Iori?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.95,0:21:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a couple unexpected guests with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.62,0:21:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, what's-their-face?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.20,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Abydos, I think?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.04,0:21:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct. The Abydos High School\nForeclosure Task Force.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.71,0:22:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother asking? The answer's\nalways going to be the same, Chinatsu.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.51,0:22:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who interferes with our official duties...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:07.22,0:22:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{=5}is an enemy.

